# 🚗 Car Rental Landing Page

## 📖 Laboratory Work - Web Development
This project is part of a **university laboratory work** focusing on **HTML & CSS**. The goal is to create a functional and visually appealing landing page for a **Car Rental Service**.

---
## 📌 Project Requirements
The landing page must:
- ✅ Include at least **6 sections** (Home, About Us, Fleet, Pricing, Testimonials, Contact).
- ✅ Have **smooth navigation** with clickable links.
- ✅ Feature a **modern and responsive design**.
- ✅ Use **Vanilla HTML & CSS** (No frameworks allowed).
- ✅ Be **deployed on a free hosting platform**.
- ✅ Have a **README.md file** with detailed documentation.

---
## 📂 Project Structure
```
📁 CarRentalLanding/
├── 📄 index.html        # Main HTML file
├── 🎨 styles.css        # CSS for styling
├── 📂 images/           # Contains all images
├── 📂 screenshots/      # Screenshots for README
└── 📄 README.md         # Documentation
```

---
## 🎨 Features
- **Fixed Navigation Bar**: Ensures easy access to all sections.
- **Hero Section**: Engaging intro with a call-to-action button.
- **Fleet Showcase**: Displays rental cars with pricing.
- **Pricing Section**: Lists rental rates for different car types.
- **Testimonials**: Customer reviews for credibility.
- **Modern Contact Form**: Collects inquiries efficiently.
- **Responsive Design**: Works on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

---
## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML5** - Page structure.
- **CSS3** - Styling and responsiveness.
- **GitHub Pages / Netlify / Vercel** - Deployment.

